# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Foundry Environment Variables Template
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# For local development:
#   1. Copy this file and rename it to `.env`
#   2. Fill in the required values
#
# We provide default values so you can start prototyping out of the box,
# but get your own API keys for production apps.
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🚨 DEPLOYER PRIVATE KEY (Server-Side Only)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used to sign contract deployments. On local Anvil chain, this can be empty
# since we use the prefunded account that comes with Anvil.
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING:
#   - NEVER commit actual private keys to git
#   - This value is auto-filled when you run `yarn generate`
#   - For production, use a hardware wallet or secure key management
#
# DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY=0x...


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔗 BLOCKCHAIN RPC PROVIDER
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Alchemy API key for RPC connections when deploying to testnets/mainnets.
# Used in foundry.toml for network configuration.
#
# Get your key at: https://dashboard.alchemy.com/
#
ALCHEMY_API_KEY=oKxs-03sij-U_N0iOlrSsZFr29-IqbuF


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔍 CONTRACT VERIFICATION
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Etherscan API key for verifying deployed contracts on block explorers.
# Required for source code verification on Etherscan, Basescan, etc.
#
# Get your key at: https://etherscan.io/myapikey
# For Base: https://basescan.org/myapikey
#
ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=DNXJA8RX2Q3VZ4URQIWP7Z68CJXQZSC6AW


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 💻 LOCAL DEVELOPMENT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default account for localhost deployments.
# Options:
#   - "scaffold-eth-default" - Uses the default Anvil prefunded account
#   - "scaffold-eth-custom"  - Use a generated or imported account
#
LOCALHOST_KEYSTORE_ACCOUNT=scaffold-eth-default
